Privacy Policy for MeowFlex
Effective Date: December 24, 2024

At MeowFlex, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you access or use our services, including our website, mobile applications, and related features (collectively referred to as "the Service").

By using our Service, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data in accordance with this policy.

1. Information We Collect
We collect the following types of information when you interact with our Service:

1.1 Personal Identification Information
When you create an account, log in, or interact with our Service, we may collect the following personal details:

Name

Email address

Phone number (optional)

Username and password

Social media login details (e.g., Facebook, Google)

1.2 Device Information
We collect data about the device you use to access our Service, including:

Device type (smartphone, tablet, computer)

IP address

Operating system

Browser type

Geolocation (if enabled)

1.3 Usage Information
We collect data about how you interact with our Service, including:

The movies and TV shows you watch

Time spent on the Service

Search queries

Content preferences

Interaction with advertisements and promotions

1.4 Cookies and Tracking Technologies
We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance user experience, analyze trends, track users' movements across the site, and gather demographic information. You can disable cookies through your browser settings, but this may limit your ability to use certain features of our Service.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To provide, maintain, and improve our Service

To personalize content, recommendations, and advertisements

To send you transactional emails (e.g., account confirmation, password resets)

To communicate with you about updates, promotions, or news related to the Service

To analyze usage patterns to improve the performance and usability of our Service

To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights and interests

3. How We Share Your Information
We may share your information with the following parties:

Service Providers: Third-party companies and individuals who help us operate our Service (e.g., payment processors, analytics providers).

Advertising Partners: To deliver personalized ads and promotions, we may share non-personal information with advertisers.

Legal Compliance: We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to legal processes (e.g., court orders, subpoenas).

We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data to third parties.

4. Data Security
We take the security of your personal information seriously. We implement a variety of security measures to protect your data, including encryption, secure servers, and regular security audits. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

5. Data Retention
We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. If you delete your account or request that we stop processing your data, we will comply with your request, subject to any legal or contractual obligations.

6. Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:

Access: You can request access to the personal data we hold about you.

Correction: You can request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.

Deletion: You can request deletion of your personal data, subject to certain exceptions.

Opt-out of Marketing: You can opt out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in those emails.

To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at [meowmeowflex@gmail.com].

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. If we make significant changes, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice on our Service. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your personal data, please contact us at:

Email: [meowmeowflex@gmail.com]
Website: [https://www.meowflex.com]
